&lt;p&gt;You will be fully accountable for steering the multi-year long-term innovation pipeline, driving macro-level category strategy in partnership with Brand, and guiding a dedicated team of in-house chemists to concept, develop, and optimize award-winning products. The Senior Director will ensure all initiatives seamlessly deliver on the company&#39;s shared category strategic vision, uncompromising quality standards, and aggressive business growth objectives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who we are looking for:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Honest Company is expanding our Research and Development leadership team! We’re looking for a strategic, visionary, and highly experienced Senior Director of Product Development. As a Senior Director in the Research and Development department, you will serve as the principal strategic leader and primary executive liaison between Research and Development and the cross-functional leadership of the operating units—including Brand, Operations, Sales, and Marketing Communications.&lt;/p&gt;
