&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Vision &amp;amp; Portfolio Leadership:&lt;/strong&gt; Partner directly with Brand and Executive leadership to architect, cultivate, and champion the long-term innovation pipeline and overarching strategic vision for Honest Baby Personal Care, Adult Personal Care, and future adjacent categories.&lt;/li&gt;
